metadata.name: Moon Birds Non Pixelated#1
metadata.description: A collection of 5,000 utility-enabled PFPs built on ERC 721A Smart Contract with richly diverse and unique non-pixelated traits. What's More, each bird unlocks additional eligibility to win an Official Moon Birds NFT, For more details check our roadmap, Minting @ 0.01 ETH, Launching on 11th May 2022, 10:00 PM UTC.
